emuInput.TitMainTitle: Harry Washington presenting trophy to Byron Peters, with Henry Smith Jr. looking on, posed in interior during FROGS symposium
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1960, pg. A2 reads: "Original Frog - Harry Washington, right, a member of the famous Frogs Club for many years, presents a trophy to Byron Peters, one of the original Frogs, as President Henry Smith Jr. (center) looks on. The presentation was made at teh symposium on Sunday, which began the annual Frog Week celebration of the club's 50th anniversary. - Harris Photo."
